{"tid":1158921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回鄉證升呢 港人可北人掛號就醫看病","createTime":"2019-05-17T10:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T15:18:46.000Z","uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"508dfaa6231b30c35347323c0925343854465f2b","tid":1158921,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:06:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2139433/回鄉證10月升呢+可內地掛號就醫證券開戶\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2139433%2F%E5%9B%9E%E9%84%89%E8%AD%8910%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%87%E5%91%A2%2B%E5%8F%AF%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%9B%E8%99%9F%E5%B0%B1%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=2741c768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2139433/回鄉證10月升呢+可內地掛號就醫證券開戶</a><br />\n<br />\n內地政府繼去年9月，准許在大陸居住半年以上的港澳居民申領居住證後，國家移民管理局昨進一步向港澳居民提供便利平台。今年10月起，憑回鄉證可在9個範圍共30多項公共民生服務獲得方便，處理上與內地居民等同，包括就醫掛號、買保險、考試報名，和辦理銀行、證券、手機開戶，及即時註冊開通網絡支付等金融理財事項。"},{"pid":"409a5d734adfc69ffc0c809a6877b733b067fd06","tid":1158921,"uid":25635,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"係咪安樂死嘅一個選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13f885ec7e2c1511e6e55a0a9d9536ef61bb4ee","tid":1158921,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"409a5d734adfc69ffc0c809a6877b733b067fd06","tid":1158921,"uid":25635,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"係咪安樂死嘅一個選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5281aaba4fd68fd490c2e5c9b8740a06b67e51f","tid":1158921,"uid":152476,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"支那人狗衝香港睇醫生<br />\n香港人就上去睇<br />\